Joan Dixon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joan_Dixon 0 Joan Dixon (June 6, 1930 in Norfolk, Virginia – February 20, 1992 in Los Angeles) was an American film and television actress in the 1950s. She is known for her role in the film noir Roadblock (1951).
